The defendant Cassie L Bigham was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Cassie L Bigham is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Cassie L Bigham was found guilty of Possess Drug Paraphernalia, an unclassified misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 961.573(1).
